            { _type: "block", style: "normal", children: [{ _type: "span", text: "Navigating the transition from 2013 to 2022 while maintaining daily business operations is a heavy lift. Our compliance architects utilize proven transition matrices and policy templates to guarantee a zero-friction upgrade." }] }
